[normal]e the view that pornography is that sexual material which is in some proven way harmful to society by its influence on adults or children. Thus, accepted sex and health educational material is not pornographic, nor are images of the naked human in Naturist
[normal],
[normal] 
[normal]Artistic, Scientific and Medical
[normal] contexts.
[normal]&#xa0;
